{"id":20640, "kind":"Bug", "createdAt":"2013-01-30T10:18:35.838006-08:00", "status":"Closed", "title":"QConsole tab-preview tooltip should have a delay", "category":"Query Console", "severity":"Aesthetic", "priority":{"level":"5", "title":""}, "submittedBy":{"username":"nwalsh", "name":"Norman Walsh", "email":"norman.walsh@marklogic.com"}, "assignTo":{"username":"nobody", "name":"nobody nobody", "email":"nobody@marklogic.com"}, "description":"The QConsole tab-preview tooltip pops up instantly, it would be nicer if it had a short delay.\r\n", "samplequery":"", "sampledata":"", "version":"6.0-1", "tofixin":"5.0-5", "fixedin":"5.0-5", "platform":"all", "memory":"", "processors":"", "note":"", "subscribers":[{"username":"nwalsh", "name":"Norman Walsh", "email":"norman.walsh@marklogic.com"}, {"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, {"username":"myawitz", "name":"Mitch Yawitz", "email":"mitchell.yawitz@marklogic.com"}, {"username":"msarma", "name":"Meghalim Sarma", "email":"msarma@marklogic.com"}, {"username":"sreddy", "name":"Sudhakar Reddy", "email":"sreddy@marklogic.com"}], "attachments":[], "relationships":[{"type":"", "to":""}], "clones":[], "cloneOf":"", "support":{"headline":"", "supportDescription":"", "publishStatus":"Never Publish", "tickets":[], "customerImpact":{"level":"N/A", "title":""}, "workaround":""}, "tags":["Query Console", "nwalsh"], "changeHistory":[{"time":"2013-01-30T10:18:35.838006-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"nwalsh", "name":"Norman Walsh", "email":"norman.walsh@marklogic.com"}, "change":{"assignTo":{"from":{"username":"nwalsh", "name":"Norman Walsh", "email":"norman.walsh@marklogic.com"}, "to":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}}}, "files":[], "show":true}, {"time":"2013-01-30T10:22:08.699743-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"myawitz", "name":"Mitch Yawitz", "email":"mitchell.yawitz@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"We should follow the standard behavior for browser-based tooltips (especially if we've rolled our own)."}, {"time":"2013-02-04T09:33:50.659389-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"Each browser has it's own way of doing tooltips, with varying delays and tooltip lifetimes. I'll start with implementing a minimum 500ms delay, which is roughly what most browsers seem to use. I couldn't find any definitive source on exact browser standards outside of the usual complaints that browsers are not consistent and are quite buggy around tooltips.\r\n\r\ntldr;\r\nThere is no standard behavior for browser-based tooltips. I'll put in a minimum 500ms delay."}, {"time":"2013-02-04T09:33:50.659389-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{"status":{"from":"", "to":"Fix"}, "assignTo":{"from":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "to":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}}}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"Each browser has it's own way of doing tooltips, with varying delays and tooltip lifetimes. I'll start with implementing a minimum 500ms delay, which is roughly what most browsers seem to use. I couldn't find any definitive source on exact browser standards outside of the usual complaints that browsers are not consistent and are quite buggy around tooltips.\r\n\r\ntldr;\r\nThere is no standard behavior for browser-based tooltips. I'll put in a minimum 500ms delay."}, {"time":"2013-02-04T10:02:22.296926-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"myawitz", "name":"Mitch Yawitz", "email":"mitchell.yawitz@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"Don't browsers show tooltips for the alt or title tags without doing anything special? Why aren't we just relying on that default behavior?"}, {"time":"2013-02-04T10:27:56.786704-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"because we're dynamically loading info with a json request to fill that preview. we can't do that natively in browser tooltips for many reasons. one big one is that some browsers don't respect /n or /r characters, so you can't put line breaks into their tooltips, which would render the preview fairly illegible.\r\n\r\nEach browser has it's own tooltip behavior and eccentricities vis a vis interaction behavior like how long it lasts, whether it stays open when you mouse over the tooltip, and usually a fair number of bugs in the interaction."}, {"time":"2013-02-04T13:46:55.547721-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "comment":"the current delay is 350ms. Let me know if it should be longer, and by how much."}, {"time":"2013-02-04T15:25:46.183635-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "svn":{"repository":"/project/engsvn", "revision":"130596", "paths":["xdmp/trunk/src/Apps/qconsole/static/js/qconsole.js"], "affectedBugs":[]}, "comment":"Bug:20640 - changed delay to 500ms from 350ms, also disabled tooltip on active tab"}, {"time":"2013-02-04T15:28:20.186686-08:00", "updatedBy":{"username":"ctaylor", "name":"Christophe Taylor", "email":"christophe.taylor@marklogic.com"}, "change":{}, "files":[], "show":true, "svn":{"repository":"/project/engsvn", "revision":"130597", "paths":["xdmp/branches/b6_0/src/Apps/qconsole/static/js/qconsole.js"], "affectedBugs":[]}, "comment":"Bug:20640 - changed delay to 500ms from 350ms, also disabled tooltip on active tab"}, {"time":"2013-02-04T15:29:57.551459-08:00", "upda